{"tid":2196293,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想砍掉重練個胃","createTime":"2020-09-09T19:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T20:41:03.000Z","uid":147970,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c95fcdc2d0825dfa3369ebfddb29538741e4c016","tid":2196293,"uid":147970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T19:15:03.000Z","msg":"成日消化不良 食少少就想嘔翻曬出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大淨係可以行路/搭屋企人車 因為入面有聞開嘅香薰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時連屋企人車我都作嘔 好短車程都覺得難頂<br />\n其實我都好鐘意搭巴士慢慢一站到下一站嘅感覺 但一搭超過15分鐘車程就會反胃 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小巴的士就更加唔掂 chok到我頭暈到要半日先回到神<br />\n我個胃到底係想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1a58327891c2a0276e80fc31add746db413a12","tid":2196293,"uid":147970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T19:16:01.000Z","msg":"有諗過係咪對眼見到嘅嘢係郁同身體唔郁嘅discrepancy 但就算瞇埋眼都係頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a5fa7d6c3c009b80be48b9b1fdfb518eb6380c","tid":2196293,"uid":147970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T19:17:06.000Z","msg":"好記得有次搭的士 30分鐘車程趕住去考試 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />落車之後即刻嘔"},{"pid":"b1f6d61e93ee5fc25224294bcc257dfc527f4eaa","tid":2196293,"uid":147970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T19: